UGQUGQUZELE ubumbano phakathi kwezinhlanga ezihlukahlukene e-United States, nasemhlabeni jikelele, uMengameli uBarack Obama ngenkathi ethula inkulumo yakhe yokugcina njengomengameli wakuleliya lizwe ngoLwesibili, eChicago . U-Obama ubekhuluma okokugcina njengomengameli nabantu base-United States njengoba isikhundla sobumengameli sesizothathwa uDonald Trump, ohlule uHillary Clinton okhethweni ngonyaka owedlule. UGQUGQUZELE ubumbano phakathi kwezinhlanga ezihlukahlukene e-United States, nasemhlabeni jikelele, uMengameli uBarack Obama ngenkathi ethula inkulumo yakhe yokugcina njengomengameli wakuleliya lizwe ngoLwesibili, eChicago . U-Obama ubekhuluma okokugcina njengomengameli nabantu base-United States njengoba isikhundla sobumengameli sesizothathwa uDonald Trump, ohlule uHillary Clinton okhethweni ngonyaka owedlule. Emva konyaka ka-2016 obunezigameko eziningi zokucwasana ngokwebala e-US, u-Obama usebenzise inkulumo yakhe yokugcina ukugqugquzela abantu baseMelika ukuthi babekezelelane. Uxwayise abantu ukuthi imthetho iyodwa ngeke ibenze babekezelelane. Kumele kuguquke izinhliziyo, usho kanje. Ucele abantu abamnyama, ababizwa ngama African-American ukuthi babekezelelane nabantu abamhlophe.&quot; Nabantu abamhlophe ngiyacela ukuthi bangabuki imibhikisho yabantu abamnyama njengempi, kodwa bayibuke njengendlela yokucela ukuphathwa ngendlela efanayo, nokuyinto eyayithenjisiwe, kuqhuba u-Obama.&nbsp;